WEBVTT

00:00:00.916 --> 00:00:06.836
A girl lies sleeping with electrodes
attached to her body.

00:00:07.556 --> 00:00:10.236
A man and a woman are looking at her

00:00:10.236 --> 00:00:13.756
through a one-way glass window
from the next room.

00:00:15.356 --> 00:00:18.276
“Waste of time and money,” says the man.

00:00:18.276 --> 00:00:21.236
“An illiterate kid from a stone quarry?

00:00:21.516 --> 00:00:24.276
What could she possibly
contribute to the project?”

00:00:25.636 --> 00:00:26.716
“Hardly a kid.

00:00:26.716 --> 00:00:29.436
She’s at least 16,” says the woman.

00:00:29.596 --> 00:00:31.596
“Come on, we’re making history.